Nacha da punjab, delhi toh karachi

Ve bombay wale kehnde mainu chadh de america
Kade uk wale kehnde aaja jina lai le paisa
Canada wich gallan hundiya, nal mere roj navi kudiyan sondiya
Sohni meri diwani, mere ware neyare
Kehndi double xl wich padiya main tere bare
Pind mera california, bohemia... te hun sari duniya ch naa
Mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga...
Bohemia main punjabi rap star, lab ke vakhao mere warga munda, lab ke vakhao mere warga, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga.bohemia mera duniya ch naa, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga, munda lab ke vakhao mere warga, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga... bohemia main punjabi rap star, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga munda, lab ke vakhao mere warga, mainu lab ke vakhao mere warga

Lab ke vakhao mere warga... lab ke vakhao mere warga...
Punjabi rap da badshah...

Nachdi sohni jiven nache kala naag
Raja bajaye been, been da rag sun billo tu nache
Ve aapan daru de raje, ve kudiyan batheri mere piche
Ve rabb mera saath de, aapan studio ch lage sari raat de
Jadon likhda main geet likhan geet soch ke
Diwani mere kallan mainu kise toh roch ke
Ve zehar pilan gayien chaa ch dobke
Ve goliyan chala gayien neher ch dobke
Ve jo oh bohemia nu marde, rabb kare mere yaar mera saath de
Ve mainu mere purane geet mere yaad rehan
Sada pardes ch desi abaad rehan, ahh yeah
Billo main tere naal viyah ni karana
Mere naal nach laih te nach laih, mera ki janda
